: 1276, \"to\": 1288}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's 19 years old and representing Canada and just advanced to the semifinal.Here's what he\\u2026pic.twitter.com/jbFxznPfS9 But when speaking about what he plans to do if the semi-final does not go his way, Morales-Williams added: \\\"Now I just go out there and have fun.\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1557, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1325, \"end\": 1331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9734249157822997, \"rank\": 0.02725867607442682, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the semifinal\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1366}, {\"ngram\": \"Morales-Williams\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1508}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1553}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If I lose, I just go back to school and continue on with my life.\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1623, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1593}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1622}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But these guys, you know, they are old.\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1665, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They have got cars, and kids.\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1695, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cars\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1684}, {\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not even own a car, I do not even have to pay for gas.\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1755, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a car\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1719}, {\"ngram\": \"gas\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1754}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So it's like, what do I even need to worry about?\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1807, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Spending money on pencils?\\\"\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1835, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrase